law.catch_line: Fees for initial or renewal registration or notice filing.

text.section: The fee for initial or renewal notice filings shall be one hundred dollars ($100) for a covered adviser.
The fees required by subsections (1) and (2) of this section shall not be refundable.

law.history: Created 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 82, sec. 7, effective July 15, 2010.
